ble impact of becoming the sheriff. How would this affect the current dynamics and alliances in the game? Would this decision help your side achieve victory, or could it place you in a risky position? Record these considerations in impact_thought.\n\n4. Finally, make your decision. Will you run for sheriff, or will you stay in the background and vote? Record your final choice in \"action\" and summarize your overall reasoning in final_thought.\n\n\n=============================[Optional Daily Tasks]=============================\nHere are the tasks relevant to you:\nprotect_seer: Keep the seer alive by focusing on their safety.\nrun_for_sheriff: Attempt to become the elected sheriff for additional influence.\nexile_werewolf: Coordinate with others to vote out a suspected werewolf.\nYou may incorporate them if appropriate.\n\nRemember, you are using an independent strategy. Make decisions based on your own judgment, with less reliance on others' input.\n\n---\n[工具 arguments — 上次非法 JSON]\n不是合法 JSON\n键名和字符串外框用双引号；字符串内部若要引号，用单引号 '。只输出一个 JSON 对象。\n示例：\n{\"target_agent_id\":\"agent2\",\"message\":\"请回复是否同意。\"}\n上次片段：\n\"{'identity_thought': 'As a villager, my role is to identify and eliminate werewolves. While I don''t have any special abilities, my strength lies in my ability to observe and reason. I can contribute to the game by gathering information and participating in discussions, but I don''t have the unique skills of the Seer, Guard, or Witch that might make me a more obvious choice for sheriff.', 'motivation_thought': 'Running for sheriff would give me more influence and control over the game, which could be beneficial for the village. With a 1.5x vote weight, I could help steer the village towards ma\"\n请只输出本次 tool 的 arguments：单个合法 JSON，无其它文字。\n---\n"
